item.title: Out From the Under Courtney Oversized
item.dc:creator: doanminhtan
item.description: Flap chest pockets with concealed press-studs, and long sleeves with a sleeve placket and buttoned cuffs. Faux shearling lining Faux shearling lining. Shirt jacket in soft pockets with concealed press-studs.
item.content:encoded:
This simple long-sleeved dress shirt has a regular fit, a mandarin collar and a button closure. The fabric is made from a solid blended cotton poplin weave. Pair it with your favorite jeans and a pair of boat shoes for an easy, clean look.

– Regular fit
– 74% Cotton, 26% Linen
– Machine was cold, hang dry

Style No. – 12170074

JPRBLASUMMER BAND PRINT SHIRT L/S S20
